<br>
The reason I do this, on occasion, is because, well, it's a helluva lotta fun.  Now, I feel that if you resort to drugs or alchohol to *have* fun, then that is a problem.  If it's one of the things you do, occasionally -- like getting drunk -- then it's fine.  I believe *anything* is bad if you do it too much.  Drugs.  Alchohol.  Sex.  Eq.  Eating.  Sleeping. <br>
<br>
But in moderation?  Hell most things are fine.  Just play it smart, use your head, and don't abuse what you use.  God taht sounded like a commercial.  I'll give you a quick list of things that are so much more fun high, you wonder why you hadn't tried the stuff earlier =p<br>
